textBox.richText: So, from now on I'll be posting whenever I upload photos from L.I.S.A (Live in Studio A), which should be around weekly/ whenever I get around to it. Direct link for L.I.S.A 10/9/08: http://169.237.101.92/archives/2008-10-09_628_192kbps.mp3 Norcal Noisefest Showcase The Norcal Experimental Music Festival was started in 1995. The first event was held at the Guild Theatre in Sacramento, on November 3rd, & 4th. Performers came from all over the western US & Canada. 2008 marks the 13th anniversary of NOISEFEST happening in the Sacramento area.
